{"comments":"Thin film interference layer for MaterialX Standard Surface.\n\nThe thin film layer provides iridescent effects caused by light\ninterference in thin coatings. Used for soap bubbles, oil slicks,\nbeetle shells, and coated optics.\n\n## MaterialX Parameters (from standard_surface.mtlx)\n\n- thin_film_thickness: [0.0, inf) default 0.0 — film thickness in nm\n- thin_film_IOR: [1.0, 3.0] default 1.5 — film index of refraction\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Complete thin film interference configuration.\n\nFor soap bubbles, oil slicks, beetle shells, and coated optics.\nThe thin film modifies the specular reflection with interference colors.\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["thickness",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Material","StandardSurface","ThinFilm"],"ThinFilmThickness"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["ior",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Spatial","Material","StandardSurface","ThinFilm"],"ThinFilmIOR"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[101,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Spatial/Material/StandardSurface/ThinFilm.purs","start":[98,1]},"title":"ThinFilm"},{"children":[],"comments":"Construct a thin film layer with all parameters.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"T